name: remnants of suburbia
description: The town of Talent, Oregon, USA, was leveled by fires. It was arson, a man was indicted and charged. Now, you can almost hear the silence of the remnants of this suburban place of respite. What stands is a world displaced. Shot on vintage Canon AE-1 camera with Portra 400 film, scan created directly from the negative. 3130 x 2075 px
